  "body_html": "<p data-start=\"264\" data-end=\"418\">✨ <strong data-start=\"266\" data-end=\"275\">Vibe:</strong><br data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"278\">Cozy, creamy, and sweet — think warm skin, soft sweaters, and golden hour light. It’s comforting but still sexy in a subtle, intimate way.</p>\n<p data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"435\">💛 <strong data-start=\"423\" data-end=\"433\">Notes:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"436\" data-end=\"528\">\n<li data-start=\"436\" data-end=\"464\">\n<p data-start=\"438\" data-end=\"464\"><strong data-start=\"438\" data-end=\"446\">Top:</strong> Whipped Vanilla</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"494\">\n<p data-start=\"467\" data-end=\"494\"><strong data-start=\"467\" data-end=\"478\">Middle:</strong> Soft Cashmere</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"495\" data-end=\"528\">\n<p data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"528\"><strong data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"506\">Base:</strong> Creamy Amber &amp; Musk</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"714\">🌙 <strong data-start=\"533\" data-end=\"550\">When to wear:</strong><br data-start=\"550\" data-end=\"553\">Perfect for <strong data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"582\">everyday wear</strong>, lounging days, or layering with other scents to add a creamy vanilla base. It’s your go-to for that “clean but warm” scent vibe.</p>",
